Canada Signs Agreement With Brazil Aiming to Increase Air Transport Links

-- B y   A n d r e w   M a y e d a
-- 
2011-08-08T15:31:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-08/canada-signs-agreement-with-brazil-aiming-to-increase-air-transport-links.html
Canada and Brazil have signed an
agreement aimed at increasing air transportation links between
the two countries, Prime Minister  Stephen Harper  said.  “Brazil is a major global economic player and a key
priority market for Canada,” Harper said in a statement posted
on his website after he met with Brazilian President Dilma
Rousseff.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Mayeda in Brasilia at 
 amayeda@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Badertscher at 
 pbadertscher@bloomberg.net  